The Gender-Based Analysis Plus was completed in January 2024. To strengthen equity and inclusivity in future assessments, upcoming surveys will incorporate optional demographic questions, engage participants with diverse professional experience, and ensure bilingual feedback collection.

Planned next steps include:
• Initiating the collection of segmented feedback immediately;
• Expanding participation in January 2025 to capture a broader range of perspectives;
• Establishing a continuous monitoring framework to uphold accessibility and inclusivity throughout the system’s lifecycle.
